    "methodology": "Maintenance backlog figures represent the estimated cost to return all local authority-maintained highway bridges in England to a state of good repair. Weight-restricted bridges are those with posted weight limits below the standard 40/44-tonne HGV limit. Substandard percentage represents bridges rated below Principal Inspection standard by local highway authorities. Regional breakdowns are based on local authority returns to DfT. Figures exclude Highways England (now National Highways) trunk road and motorway structures.",
